caption: tides will forever be my favorite Jack and Jack song. as they make new songs I love each and every one but tides is honestly the one that has had the greatest effect on me. It never fails to make me see the light in every situation no matter what it is. each song speaks to me in a different way and tides is just the one that I connect with the most. around Christmas is the best time to be grateful for everything in my life and Jack and Jack are definitely in the top five.  @jackandjackofficial
